# 100 Dollars Reward.  
Ran away from the subscriber, living in Lincoln county, about the 8th November last, a NEGRO MAN, known by the name of GEORGE BLACKSTONE. He is tolerably dark complected, and wishes to be very polite in company; is between 35 and 40 years of age, has a thin visage, with large whiskers, and has lost two fo his fore teeth, which causes an impediment in his sppech; he i snear 6 feet high, and weighs about 1080. Fifty Dollars reward will be given for securing him in any jail in this state, so that I get him again; of is apprehended out of the state, a reward of One Hundred Dollars will be given.  
WILLIAM OWSLEY.  
